channel.title: Please help!
channel.description:
Hello people. I'm using Galkon's client and I've recently made some interface edits to it and etc.
Now i'm using a blank Emulous base with it... but the prayer headicons don't work. I did Galkon's tutorial on r-s on loading them... but it messes up. Like if I click protect from melee it brings up protect from magic and etc.
Please help me! And if anyone could tell me which source I should use with this client, I'd be very grateful!
